statements.sql:
SELECT o.id_order, os.date_departure, os.time_departure,
ho.observation, ho.id_order_status, concat(dr.first_name," ",dr.last_name) as conductor, osd.placa, os.description  FROM orders o
INNER JOIN history_orders ho ON ho.id_order=o.id_order
INNER JOIN order_schedules os ON os.id_order=o.id_order
INNER JOIN order_schedule_details osd ON osd.id_order_schedule=os.id_order_schedule
INNER JOIN drivers dr on dr.nid_driver=osd.nid_driver
WHERE (ho.id_order_status=8 or ho.id_order_status=11)  and osd.placa='LEI654'  AND ho.`status`=1
and os.date_departure>='2020-07-01' and os.date_departure<='2020-07-31'
group by o.id_order ORDER BY os.date_departure desc
